            <h1>How / why was my business selected?</h1>
            <p>We select businesses from the Inter-Departmental Business Register (IDBR). The IDBR is a register of businesses in the UK registered for PAYE, VAT or with Companies House.</p>

            <p>Selection depends on several factors. For example, the number of people employed, how many other businesses are operating in the same industry and the size of those businesses.</p>

            <p>We always include large businesses in the survey sample because the information they provide can be significant.</p>

            <p>Large businesses are usually defined as having over 100 employees.</p>
            <h2>Did this answer your question?</h2>
            <p class="field">
                <div class="btn-group">
                {{ 
                    onsButton({
                        "type": 'button',
                        "text": 'Yes',
                        "classes": 'btn-group__btn',
                        "url": "/prototypes/user-self-serve/version-7/00-surveys-list.html"
                    }) 
                }}
                {{ 
                    onsButton({
                        "type": 'button',
                        "text": 'No',
                        "classes": 'btn--secondary btn-group__btn',
                        "url": "send-message.html"
                    }) 
                }}
                </div>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

